:61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T21:05:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"62718bde77730388e521767d9b83f7b2d24d645d","tid":1553962,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T21:08:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢炒我哋唔洗炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要重光與地球癌切割，正如手術總有點陣痛，無可能零風險！！！</span></span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49f67a83e1b9eac854299acedcfdf78f9b689bcc","tid":1553962,"uid":286792,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T21:56:29.000Z","msg":"十年前嘅國際金融風暴爆發嘅其中一個主要原因就係因為高息房屋貸款而引起<br />\n情況同依家支那有啲相似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n盲目相信房價有升無跌 進行大量投機買賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n現實係房價唔會無止境上升 有朝一日泡沫爆破 樓價急跌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家都因為樓價泡沫爆破而輸錢 唔夠現金問銀行借<br />\n銀行都冇錢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />正式進入 cash is king 嘅年代<br />\nCredit rating 低嘅公司因借唔到錢而破產<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n投資者連本金都收唔番 經濟跳崖式下降<br />\n最後金融風暴殺到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n支那唔爆都元氣大傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9d8a79efa934e10ffa625fcc7894aa3de1dc2c5","tid":1553962,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T00:54:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/ass